Package: TheMarkUSA
Title: Helper Functions for The Mark USA, INC
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zack", "Crowley", , "zcrowley@themarkusa.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("The Mark USA, INC.", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: The goal of TheMarkUSA is to make data cleaning and the
    creation of visualizations easier and faster for The Mark USA, INC.
    TheMarkUSA contains functions to create visuals with The Mark USA
    branding and helper functions for common data cleaning and
    manipulation tasks for use for everyone at The Mark USA, INC.
